****************************************************************
			H3expresso
****************************************************************

Simplified version of H3.3: A harmonic code for solving the full
Einstein Equations casted as a First Order Flux Conservative
Hyperbolic system using Advanced Numerical Methods on a cartesian 3d
grid.

Please, check the H3expresso code documentation available in the world
wide web on the following URL:

http://jean-luc.ncsa.uiuc.edu/People/Joan/H3expresso/


Contact me in case of any doubt/problem/suggestion...

	                              Joan Masso
		                      jmasso@ncsa.uiuc.edu



